Class TileList

  • java.lang.Object
    • ch.zhaw.psit.towerhopscotch.models.tiles.TileList

  • public class TileList
extends java.lang.Object
    Each tile is initialized once in the static instance list. With method getTile a tile instance can be gotten via its ID.
